Hi Karley Pines, You want like this  &lt;div class="team-field-group"&gt;
  &lt;div class="team-field"&gt;
    &lt;label for="team-name"&gt;Team Name:&lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;input type="text" id="team-name" name="team-name"&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="team-field"&gt;
    &lt;label for="team-description"&gt;Team Description:&lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;textarea id="team-description" name="team-description"&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="team-field"&gt;
    &lt;label for="team-members"&gt;Team Members:&lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;select id="team-members" name="team-members" multiple&gt;
      &lt;option value="member1"&gt;Member 1&lt;/option&gt;
      &lt;option value="member2"&gt;Member 2&lt;/option&gt;
      &lt;option value="member3"&gt;Member 3&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;/select&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
